title: Adventure Time (Ongoing + Miniseries + Extras - up to Dec 2013)
description:
Just in time for the new year, it's this massive Adventure Time collection! OH MY GLOB YOU GUYZ! Seriously, if you aren't reading these comics (or watching the show) now is the perfect time to catch up. Ryan North, the creators and some wonderful artists make this series and its offshoots one of the best on the market, regardless of age. So what are you waiting for? This torrent contains:

-Adventure Time (Ongoing Series) - issues 01-23 (2012-2013)
-Adventure Time with Fionna and Cake (Miniseries) - issues 01-06 (Complete)
-Adventure Time Presents...Marceline and the Scream Queens (Miniseries) - issues 01-06 (Complete)
-Adventure Time: Candy Capers (Miniseries) - issues 01-04 (of 6 total, last two not released yet)
-Adventure Time: Playing With Fire (TBP, Complete, 2013)
-Adventure Time 2013 Annual and 2013 Summer Special (Single Issues)

This is everything that has been produced so far except the recently released "Pixel Princesses" TBP which I have not found yet. Hope you enjoy and have a safe New Year, and always please seed! :-)

Seriously though, drop everything and plow through this now if you haven't already. And don't drive drunk!
